These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, bus
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, thai, turkish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, climbing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
2. the thai is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the thai is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| Transport   | bus       | helicopter     | roller    |
| Nationality   | turkish   | thai          | indian   |
| Sport         | badminton | skateboarding | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, cabbage, nectarine
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, collecting, video-games
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, ferret
1. the owner of the ferret is the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
3. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
5. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food    | avocado     | nectarine  | cabbage  |
| Hobby   | video-games | collecting | chess    |
| Pet     | goldfish      | ferret    | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, documentary
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, reggae
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, skiing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of funk##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre          | disaster         | documentary     | fantasy   |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop       | funk     | reggae |
| Sport         | weightlifting | lacrosse | skiing |

