.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, sports, western
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, white, yellow
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, tennis
1. the person watching sports movies is between the person who likes pink and the person watching western movies##2
2. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | sports        | western |
| Color           | pink   | white      | yellow     |
| Sport         | tennis | skateboarding | golf    |

