1. the person who growsdahlia is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person who growsaconite is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |    3    |
| Flower         | dahlia | orchid      | aconite  |
| Pet         | bird         | snake      | pony    |
| Transport   | bike         | skateboard | scooter |

