1. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
3. the modern house is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the modern house##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| House    | victorian        | modern | futuristic     |
| Sport       | basketball | golf          | water-polo |
| Transport   | subway     | tram          | boat       |

