.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, december, march
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, musical
3 different pets are kept: cat, fish, lizard
1. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person watching documentary movies##2
2. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the fish##1
5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
7. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday         | march      | december | june |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | crime      | musical    |
| Pet           | lizard      | cat        | fish       |

 